      "chunk_id": "0",
      "raw_text": "OFFER LETTER Personal and Confidential\nSeptember 5, 2024\nTo Sumit Telawane ,\nWelcome to CrossAsyst !\nIt gives us tremendous pleasure to extend our offer of employment to have you join CrossAsyst Infotech Private Limited as a Trainee -Data Engineer from 9 th September 2024 . We are confident that you will have a fulfilling and rewarding career at CrossAsyst .\nAs we have discussed previously, CrossAsyst is a leading and premier provider of IT consulting and development services in the healthcare technology space. We has created a track record of successful partnerships with startups and early stage ventures to improve healthcare through our technical leadership in the innovative and pioneering use of the latest software technologies.\nAt CrossAsyst , you will be a part of our IT solutions group. As part of this group, you will continue to have the opportunities to work on cutting edge software technologies, while also developing a broad knowledge of healthcare workflows. In addition, CrossAsyst will also present opportunities for personal development through our multi-faceted training programs, interest groups,leadership development programs, and our conscious policy of enabling all team members to be part of direct end-client communication.\nAs we have discussed, your compensation will be Rs. 3,00,000/- per annum -Rs.Three Lakhs only as fixed.\nUpon joining, we will execute an appointment letter. Once again, we welcome you to CrossAsyst and to the dynamic world of healthcare software and technology. Kindly note that this offer is contingent upon successful completion of a background check, including a check of your employment references.\nThis offer is valid till September 5 th , 2024 . Please do not hesitate to let us know if you have any queries.\nWith best wishes,\nFor CrossAsyst Infotech Private Limited\nAccepted & Confirmed",
